falign.csh can be used to generate phone  and word segmentations using the models included in this package.
Start with filling in the filenames, paths etc in the script falign.csh
Point it to the right executable in your sphinx package.
Plug in the data in the formats shown in the XXX.* files.

The models will work for mfccs computed using the sphinx mfc code, 
key settings are in the filenames of the models: lowerf=80 upperf=7200
number of filters=40
Use fft size = 512

The mfc files are assumed to be foo1.extension foo2.extension foo3.extension 
in the examples given.

Send email if you have any questions.

-Rita
